This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the segmentation of 3D shapes. It could also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it involves understanding and evaluating shapes. The use of deep learning models suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of refinement features suggests that it could also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
